ragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Happy Mother&rsquo;s Day at Buffet NINETEEN!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Savor time with the most important woman in your life at NINETEEN!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Life wouldn&rsquo;t be the same without the love and care of one&rsquo;s mother. What better way to celebrate the important relationship than with a leisure morning spent enjoying delicious foods, conversation, and laughter. Caravelle Saigon&rsquo;s Buffet NINETEEN provides a great feast of fresh seafood and catch of the day, a selection of fresh salads, roasted meats, sushi and sashimi, directly imported French cheeses, local dishes, homemade breads and international favorites as well as carefully prepared desserts. It is the perfect accompaniment to a day spent making memories with family.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Don&rsquo;t forget on upgrading to our unlimited wines or Champagne drink package for an extra exuberant atmosphere!<br \/>Happy Mother&rsquo;s Day Brunch and Dinner are available only on Sunday, 9th May 2021 with priced at VND 1,599,000++ per person including soft drink, tea &amp; coffee.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Standard Benefits for Caravelle Classique Club Members<br \/>Price is subject to 5% Service Charge &amp; 10% VAT<br \/>For more information, please call (84) 2838 234 999 or email: culinary@caravellehotel.com<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4s9a31pg buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tablecheck.com\/en\/shops\/nineteen-buffet-restaurant\/reserve\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">BOOK YOUR TABLE<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style> .ffb-id-4s9a31p8{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-4s9a31pg .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ color:#ff